   <body xml:id="thebody" style="defaultCaption">
      <div xml:lang="en">
         <p begin="00:00:02.03" end="00:00:04.40" region="speaker">The Program Administration screen will show the</p>
         <p begin="00:00:04.40" end="00:00:06.16" region="speaker">information provided.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:06.16" end="00:00:07.56" region="speaker">You may have already filled out your</p>
         <p begin="00:00:07.56" end="00:00:10.63" region="speaker">Subcontracting Plan Program Administrator and</p>
         <p begin="00:00:10.63" end="00:00:12.40" region="speaker">alternate contact information on the</p>
         <p begin="00:00:12.40" end="00:00:14.83" region="speaker">Solicitation Clauses screen.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:14.83" end="00:00:17.10" region="speaker">However, if there is no contact information</p>
         <p begin="00:00:17.10" end="00:00:19.36" region="speaker">already entered, or you need to change the</p>
         <p begin="00:00:19.36" end="00:00:22.03" region="speaker">information in there, you will need to navigate to</p>
         <p begin="00:00:22.03" end="00:00:24.70" region="speaker">the Solicitation Clauses section using the</p>
         <p begin="00:00:24.70" end="00:00:27.70" region="speaker">navigation on the left side of your screen.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:27.70" end="00:00:30.33" region="speaker">On the Solicitation Clauses screen, you will</p>
         <p begin="00:00:30.33" end="00:00:32.40" region="speaker">notice the addition of the Point of Contacts</p>
         <p begin="00:00:32.40" end="00:00:33.80" region="speaker">Information entry.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:33.80" end="00:00:36.90" region="speaker">Click the &quot;Respond&quot; link in the actions column.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:36.90" end="00:00:39.50" region="speaker">Select &quot;Contact for Subcontracting Plan&quot; from</p>
         <p begin="00:00:39.50" end="00:00:42.13" region="speaker">the dropdown menu and click &quot;Add Point of</p>
         <p begin="00:00:42.13" end="00:00:44.36" region="speaker">Contact Details.&quot;</p>
         <p begin="00:00:44.36" end="00:00:46.76" region="speaker">Fill out the administrator for the Subcontracting</p>
         <p begin="00:00:46.76" end="00:00:47.93" region="speaker">Plan.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:47.93" end="00:00:50.16" region="speaker">When you are finished click &quot;Add Point of</p>
         <p begin="00:00:50.16" end="00:00:52.13" region="speaker">Contact Information.&quot;</p>
         <p begin="00:00:52.13" end="00:00:54.10" region="speaker">While it&apos;s not required, it is a good idea to add</p>
         <p begin="00:00:54.10" end="00:00:59.00" region="speaker">an Alternative Contact for the Subcontracting Plan.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:59.00" end="00:00:60.93" region="speaker">When you have finished, return to the</p>
         <p begin="00:00:60.93" end="00:00:63.60" region="speaker">Subcontracting plan by clicking its link on the</p>
         <p begin="00:00:63.60" end="00:00:65.40" region="speaker">menu to the left.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:65.40" end="00:00:67.63" region="speaker">You will notice the Point of Contact details have</p>
         <p begin="00:00:67.63" end="00:00:69.06" region="speaker">been updated.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:69.06" end="00:00:71.23" region="speaker">Next you will need to identify the duties of the</p>
         <p begin="00:00:71.23" end="00:00:73.83" region="speaker">Subcontracting Plan administrator.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:73.83" end="00:00:76.70" region="speaker">One through five are required by the FAR.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:76.70" end="00:00:79.43" region="speaker">Select the applicable functions, meant to ensure</p>
         <p begin="00:00:79.43" end="00:00:81.90" region="speaker">effective implementation of the subcontracting</p>
         <p begin="00:00:81.90" end="00:00:82.93" region="speaker">plan.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:82.93" end="00:00:85.80" region="speaker">Identify any additional measures in the textbox at</p>
         <p begin="00:00:85.80" end="00:00:87.50" region="speaker">the end of the list.</p>
         <p begin="00:00:87.50" end="00:00:90.36" region="speaker">When you are finished click &quot;Save and Continue.&quot;</p>
    </div>
